item.description:
Have you ever wonder; how can I have multiple domains or subdomains pointing to different projects but all of them are in just one server? well&hellip;
This will be a very simple tutorial for doing that, with NGINX.
tutorial tasks:  Creating or pointing domains/subdomains to the server&rsquo;s IP address Setup NGINX Create a directory to keep the project Change folder permissions Create a simple html page to display Create a new Server Block with your domain or subdomain Setup and link the Server Block Restart NGINX  1.
